YES, I'm stating there shall be a new Oscar category for Championship Sports commercials. Even Tom Selleck's "Arkansas Toothpick" wants nothing to do with that stache. I say this and I say it LOUD AND PROUD... FUCK Lil' Nas X and the parasite that rode in on him (Really Gay Virus lol )... I ain't gonna lie and say the boom speakers as saddle bags weren't dope, but anyone who knows the history in the equine industry for "marching horses" better make sure they weren't using the salts on that animal.
